data.name: CommonFilePickerElementIds
desc: These constants are used to specify common controls of a FilePicker dialog.

items.name: PUSHBUTTON_OK
lines: The control id of the OK button.

items.name: PUSHBUTTON_CANCEL
lines: The control id of the Cancel button.

items.name: LISTBOX_FILTER
lines: The filter listbox of a FilePicker dialog.

items.name: CONTROL_FILEVIEW
lines: Is used to refer to the file view of the file picker.
This view shows the list of all files/folders in the currently selected folder.

items.name: EDIT_FILEURL
lines: Is used to refer to the edit line where a file or path can be entered by the user.

items.name: LISTBOX_FILTER_LABEL
lines: The label of the filter listbox of a FilePicker dialog.

items.name: EDIT_FILEURL_LABEL
lines: The label of the file name listbox of a FilePicker dialog.
